    *N000682,1 MMT 12/09/2012 Globalization changes[Start]
    *WAIT WINDOW 'RANGE: 0 to '+ ALLTRIM(STR(MIN(lnMax, EVALUATE(loParent.lcOrderLin + '.Qty' + lcNo)))) NOWAIT    
